reviews.review_text: I'm 25 year old..... more than 5000 burger till now..... but GD'S burger is a gem.... so delicious sooo juicy and the way he handles his burger family is a cherry on top.... superb rate and superb taste.... no more words to describe the way I felt for this place.... Gd's burger is a feeling forever now.... if you're in Goa... don't waste a minute come to this place and thank me later.
I am basically a food lover, I have visited different countries and almost all states in India, every time I'll be experiencing and this time here comes in goa with GD's burger ❤️
Best place for burger. don’t miss this place ever.
